Biomatrix seen posting Q4 oper profit - report . Biomatrix Inc is seen generating an operating profit by the fourth quarter of 1997 , a Business Week article said . Len Bogner , former Prudential Securities analyst who now runs BGS Associates , told Business Week he expected Biomatrix to post an operating profit , exclusive of royalties , licensing and other fees , by the fourth quarter . Bogner said he expected Biomatrix ' s share price to reach $ 25 by year - end and $ 50 in 18 months , the June 30 issue of the magazine said . Biomatrix develops and manufactures products made from series of proprietary biological polymers used in therapeutic medical applications . Shares of Biomatrix were 1 - 7 / 8 higher at 18 - 7 / 8 early Friday afternoon . 
